  "prompt": "What is the average and highest package of Galgotia University Noida?",
  "response": "As of my latest information up to October 2023, **Galgotias University** in Noida has maintained a commendable placement record across various disciplines. Here's a general overview of their placement statistics:\n\n### **Average Package:**\n- **B.Tech and Engineering Courses:** The average annual package typically ranges between **\u20b94 lakhs to \u20b98 lakhs**.\n- **Management Programs (like MBA):** Students often secure average packages in the range of **\u20b96 lakhs to \u20b912 lakhs** per annum.\n- **Other Disciplines (e.g., Computer Applications, Hospitality):** Average packages vary but generally fall between **\u20b93 lakhs to \u20b97 lakhs** annually.\n\n### **Highest Package:**\n- **Top Incentive Offers:** Galgotias University has seen maximum packages reaching up to **\u20b945 lakhs to \u20b950 lakhs** per annum. These high packages are usually offered by prominent multinational companies and leading tech firms.\n  \n### **Key Recruiters:**\nSome of the major recruiters that regularly participate in Galgotias University's placement drives include:\n- **Technology Firms:** Amazon, Microsoft, Google, Adobe, Infosys, TCS, and Accenture.\n- **Consulting and Finance:** Deloitte, EY, KPMG, and various investment banks.\n- **Core Engineering Companies:** Larsen & Toubro, Siemens, and Bharat Heavy Electricals Limited (BHEL).\n- **Startups and Other Sectors:** A variety of startups and companies across different sectors also participate, offering diverse opportunities to students.\n\n### **Placement Support:**\nGalgotias University provides robust placement support through:\n- **Dedicated Placement Cell:** Assisting students with resume building, interview preparation, and soft skills training.\n- **Workshops and Seminars:** Regular sessions conducted to enhance employability skills.\n- **Internship Opportunities:** Facilitating internships which often serve as a pathway to full-time employment.\n\n### **Note:**\n- **Variation by Year and Course:** Placement statistics can vary annually based on factors like economic conditions, industry demand, and the specific batch's performance.\n- **Individual Performance:** Personal skills, internships, projects, and academic performance significantly influence placement outcomes.\n\nFor the most accurate and updated placement statistics, it's advisable to:\n- **Visit the Official Galgotias University Placement Page:** [Galgotias University Placements](https://www.galgotiasuniversity.edu.in/academics/placements/)\n- **Contact the Placement Cell Directly:** They can provide detailed reports and insights specific to your course and year of graduation.\n\nFeel free to reach out if you have more specific questions or need further assistance!",
